drug.absorption:
Degarelix forms a depot at the site of injection after subcutaneous administration from which the drug slowly released into circulation. After a single bolus dose of 2mg/kg, peak plasma concentrations of degarelix occured within 6 hours at a concentration of 330 ng/mL. 
Ki = 0.082 ng/mL and 93% of receptors were fully suppressed; 
MRT = 4.5 days.

drug.half-life:
Terminal half-life: 41.5 - 70.2 days; 
Absorption half-life: 32.9 hours; 
Half-life from injection site: 1.17 days.
